data.title: The Story Games Names Project
data.meta_description: A collection of names and related lists from dozens of different cultures, times, and places.  Everything from Maori, Russian, and Chinese to Hobo.
data.text:
Mexican Cinema

Compiled by Jason Morningstar

Actually Mexican wrestling-horror-science fiction movies. All the personal names refer to real people, and yes, Boris Karloff did appear in La Muerta Viviente!
